casebody.data:
TWAN BEY (Antwan L. Burns)
v.
CUMBERLAND COUNTY DISTRICT COURT, Robert J. Stiehl. No. 201P15. Supreme Court of North Carolina. Aug. 20, 2015. Twan (Antwan L. Burns) Bey, for Bey, Twan (Antwan L. Burns).

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Petitioner on the 16th of June 2015 in this matter for a writ of mandamus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Cumberland County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 20th of August 2015."
